programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1969 All-Star Game

programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1977 All-Star Game

programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1984 All-Star Game
programme.desc: The 1984 All-Star Game in Denver. The East outlasted the West 154-145 in overtime as Isiah Thomas earned MVP honors with 22 points and 15 assists. Julius Erving scored a game-high 34 for the winners, while Kareem Abdul-Jabbar had 25 points and 15 boards in a losing effort. (cc)(n)

programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1985 All-Star Game
programme.desc: The 1985 NBA All Star Game in Indianapolis. The West won 140-129 behind game MVP Ralph Sampson's 24 points and 10 rebounds. Magic Johnson added 21 points and 15 assists. (cc)(n)

programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1986 All-Star Game
programme.desc: The 1986 All-Star Game in Dallas. The East beat the West 139-132. Isiah Thomas earned MVP honors. (cc)(n)

programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1987 All-Star Game
programme.desc: The 1987 All-Star Game in Seattle. The West defeated the East 154-149 in overtime. Tom Chambers was MVP. (cc)(n)

programme.title: NBA Hardwood Classics: 1988 All-Star Game
